23:35.748 --> 23:48.227 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Now: the role
of America's
historically black colleges, and
what could,

23:48.260 --> 23:50.362 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
