23:50.396 --> 23:54.366 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That was on President Trump's
agenda today,
and is the focus of our weekly
segment Making

23:54.400 --> 23:56.168 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
the Grade.

23:56.201 --> 24:00.306 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
As part of an effort to
celebrate Black History
Month, President Trump signed an
executive

24:00.339 --> 24:03.475 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
order today aimed at helping
historically
black colleges and universities.

24:03.509 --> 24:08.714 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP, President of the
United States:
HBCUs have been really pillars
of the African-American

24:08.747 --> 24:16.789 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
community for more than 150
years, an amazing
job, and a grand and enduring
symbol of American

24:16.822 --> 24:18.624 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
at its absolute best.

24:18.657 --> 24:23.762 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
With this executive order, we
will make HBCUs
a priority in the White House,
an absolute

24:23.796 --> 24:25.431 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
priority.

24:25.464 --> 24:28.801 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The order will
move the
government's program for
coordinating HBCUs

24:28.834 --> 24:31.337 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
back directly under the White
House.

24:31.370 --> 24:36.942 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But the president didn't commit
any additional
funds to the schools yet, some
of which are

24:36.975 --> 24:38.744 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
