collectively.

25:30.662 --> 25:32.431 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHNNY C. TAYLOR JR., President
and CEO, Thurgood
Marshall College Fund: We should
be very clear

25:32.464 --> 25:38.070 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
that we want this administration
and the 115th
Congress to make good on the
money.

25:38.103 --> 25:40.139 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
You cannot have mission without
money.

25:40.172 --> 25:43.509 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: After
President Trump's
meeting, his education
secretary, Betsy DeVos,

25:43.542 --> 25:45.411 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
