25:45.444 --> 25:50.182 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In a statement heralding the
HBCUs, she called
them -- quote -- "real pioneers
when it comes

25:50.215 --> 25:51.850 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
