25:51.884 --> 25:55.854 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Critics say her statement
ignores the long
history of segregation for black
students

25:55.888 --> 25:59.458 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and the underfunding of black
schools.

25:59.491 --> 26:04.430 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Let's take a closer look now at
the president's
executive order and the status
of these schools.

26:04.463 --> 26:07.966 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
For that, we're joined by Johnny
Taylor, who
was at the meeting and is
president of the

26:08.000 --> 26:10.636 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
