United America."

26:17.009 --> 26:18.744 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Johnny, let me start with you.

26:18.777 --> 26:23.749 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Why is it important for this
initiative to
be back under the White House?

26:23.782 --> 26:28.120 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHNNY C. TAYLOR JR.: You know,
at the end
of the day where you live
matters in so many

26:28.153 --> 26:29.855 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
ways, right?

26:29.888 --> 26:33.459 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When we were in the Department
of Education,
this office, it was three levels
down.

26:33.492 --> 26:36.328 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It didn't even report to the
secretary of
education.

26:36.361 --> 26:42.234 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
To me, that said volumes about
what the former
administration and frankly
former administrations

26:42.267 --> 26:45.037 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
