26:45.070 --> 26:49.208 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We judge you -- more about what
you say, it's
about what you do.

26:49.241 --> 26:54.313 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so moving us to the White
House sends
the message to the entire
country that HBCUs

26:54.346 --> 26:58.450 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
matter, and they matter to the
person -- frankly,
the most powerful person in the
country, the

26:58.484 --> 26:59.451 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
president of the United States.

26:59.485 --> 27:00.819 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Sophia Nelson,
it's symbolic.

27:00.853 --> 27:02.488 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
