27:02.521 --> 27:04.256 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
But it's not cash.

27:04.289 --> 27:06.959 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And cash and funding is what a
lot of these
presidents are here lobbying for
right now.

